{
  "version": "Notebook/1.0",
  "items": [
    {
      "type": 1,
      "content": {
        "json": "# DC SYSVOL & AD Replication Health Monitor\n---\n**Classification:** UNCLASSIFIED // FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY &nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp; **Data Sources:** DFS Replication · File Replication Service · Directory Service &nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp; **Scope:** Domain Controllers with SYSVOL / NTFRS / DFSR Replication\n\nThis workbook monitors all three DCR XPath-collected event sources for SYSVOL replication health, DFSR and NTFRS status, and Active Directory Directory Service events. Use the **Time Range** selector and tabs below to explore each domain. Health banners, critical event tables, and trend charts update automatically based on the filters selected.",
        "style": "0"
      },
      "name": "banner-header"
    },
    {
      "type": 9,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "id": "param-tab",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "Tab",
            "type": 1,
            "isHiddenWhenLocked": true,
            "value": "Overview"
          },
          {
            "id": "param-timerange",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "TimeRange",
            "label": "Time Range",
            "type": 4,
            "isRequired": true,
            "typeSettings": {
              "selectableValues": [
                {
                  "durationMs": 3600000
                },
                {
                  "durationMs": 14400000
                },
                {
                  "durationMs": 43200000
                },
                {
                  "durationMs": 86400000
                },
                {
                  "durationMs": 172800000
                },
                {
                  "durationMs": 604800000
                },
                {
                  "durationMs": 2592000000
                },
                {
                  "durationMs": 7776000000
                }
              ],
              "allowCustom": true
            },
            "value": {
              "durationMs": 86400000
            }
          },
          {
            "id": "param-computers",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "Computers",
            "label": "Domain Controllers",
            "type": 2,
            "multiSelect": true,
            "quote": "'",
            "delimiter": ",",
            "query": "Event\n| where EventLog in (\"DFS Replication\",\"File Replication Service\",\"Directory Service\")\n| summarize by Computer\n| order by Computer asc\n| project Computer",
            "value": [
              "value::all"
            ],
            "typeSettings": {
              "additionalResourceOptions": [
                "value::all"
              ],
              "showDefault": false
            },
            "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
            "queryType": 0,
            "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces"
          }
        ],
        "style": "pills",
        "queryType": 0,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces"
      },
      "name": "global-parameters"
    },
    {
      "type": 11,
      "content": {
        "version": "LinkItem/1.0",
        "style": "tabs",
        "links": [
          {
            "id": "tab-overview",
            "cellValue": "Tab",
            "linkTarget": "parameter",
            "linkLabel": "Overview",
            "subTarget": "Overview",
            "style": "link"
          },
          {
            "id": "tab-dfsr",
            "cellValue": "Tab",
            "linkTarget": "parameter",
            "linkLabel": "DFS Replication",
            "subTarget": "DFSR",
            "style": "link"
          },
          {
            "id": "tab-ntfrs",
            "cellValue": "Tab",
            "linkTarget": "parameter",
            "linkLabel": "File Replication (NTFRS)",
            "subTarget": "NTFRS",
            "style": "link"
          },
          {
            "id": "tab-ds",
            "cellValue": "Tab",
            "linkTarget": "parameter",
            "linkLabel": "Directory Service",
            "subTarget": "DS",
            "style": "link"
          },
          {
            "id": "tab-socsecurity",
            "cellValue": "Tab",
            "linkTarget": "parameter",
            "linkLabel": "Security and MDE",
            "subTarget": "SOCSecurity",
            "style": "link"
          },
          {
            "id": "tab-critical",
            "cellValue": "Tab",
            "linkTarget": "parameter",
            "linkLabel": "Critical Events",
            "subTarget": "Critical",
            "style": "link"
          },
          {
            "id": "tab-dcmatrix",
            "cellValue": "Tab",
            "linkTarget": "parameter",
            "linkLabel": "DC Health Matrix",
            "subTarget": "DCMatrix",
            "style": "link"
          },
          {
            "id": "tab-logvolume",
            "cellValue": "Tab",
            "linkTarget": "parameter",
            "linkLabel": "Log Volume and Cost",
            "subTarget": "LogVolume",
            "style": "link"
          }
        ]
      },
      "name": "tabs"
    },
    {
      "type": 12,
      "name": "group-overview",
      "conditionalVisibility": {
        "parameterName": "Tab",
        "comparison": "isEqualTo",
        "value": "Overview"
      },
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "## Environment-Wide Summary\nTop-level health across all three replication event sources. **Errors / Critical** and **DFSR/NTFRS Critical** KPIs are the most actionable — any value above zero requires investigation.",
              "style": "info"
            },
            "name": "overview-header"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "overview-kpis",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "let base = Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog in (\"DFS Replication\",\"File Replication Service\",\"Directory Service\")\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers});\nlet totalEvents = toscalar(base | count);\nlet dcCount = toscalar(base | summarize dcount(Computer));\nlet errorCount = toscalar(base | where EventLevelName in (\"Error\",\"Critical\") | count);\nlet warningCount = toscalar(base | where EventLevelName == \"Warning\" | count);\nlet dfsrCriticalCount = toscalar(base | where EventLog == \"DFS Replication\" and EventID in (2213, 4012, 5002, 6016, 4002, 4004) | count);\nlet ntfrsCriticalCount = toscalar(base | where EventLog == \"File Replication Service\" and EventID in (13508, 13520, 13552, 13555, 13568, 13572) | count);\nprint Metric=\"Total Events\", Value=totalEvents\n| union (print Metric=\"DCs Reporting\", Value=dcCount)\n| union (print Metric=\"Errors / Critical\", Value=errorCount)\n| union (print Metric=\"Warning Events\", Value=warningCount)\n| union (print Metric=\"DFSR Critical\", Value=dfsrCriticalCount)\n| union (print Metric=\"NTFRS Critical\", Value=ntfrsCriticalCount)",
              "size": 4,
              "title": "Key Performance Indicators",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "tiles",
              "tileSettings": {
                "showBorder": true,
                "titleContent": {
                  "columnMatch": "Metric",
                  "formatter": 1
                },
                "leftContent": {
                  "columnMatch": "Value",
                  "formatter": 12,
                  "formatOptions": {
                    "palette": "auto"
                  },
                  "numberFormat": {
                    "unit": 17,
                    "options": {
                      "style": "decimal",
                      "maximumFractionDigits": 0
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "overview-timeline",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog in (\"DFS Replication\",\"File Replication Service\",\"Directory Service\")\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| summarize Count=count() by bin(TimeGenerated, 1h), EventLog\n| order by TimeGenerated asc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Event Volume Timeline - All Sources (per Hour)",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "areachart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "showLegend": true
              }
            }
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "overview-by-source",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog in (\"DFS Replication\",\"File Replication Service\",\"Directory Service\")\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| summarize Count=count() by EventLog",
              "size": 3,
              "title": "Events by Log Source",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "piechart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "showLegend": true
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "33"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "overview-by-severity",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog in (\"DFS Replication\",\"File Replication Service\",\"Directory Service\")\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| where isnotempty(EventLevelName)\n| summarize Count=count() by EventLevelName, EventLog\n| order by Count desc",
              "size": 3,
              "title": "Events by Severity & Source",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "barchart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "showLegend": true
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "33"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "overview-error-trend",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog in (\"DFS Replication\",\"File Replication Service\",\"Directory Service\")\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| where EventLevelName in (\"Error\",\"Critical\",\"Warning\")\n| summarize Count=count() by bin(TimeGenerated, 1h), EventLevelName\n| order by TimeGenerated asc",
              "size": 3,
              "title": "Errors & Warnings Over Time",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "linechart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "showLegend": true,
                "seriesLabelSettings": [
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Error",
                    "color": "red"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Critical",
                    "color": "redBright"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Warning",
                    "color": "yellow"
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "33"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "overview-events-by-hour-heatmap",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog in (\"DFS Replication\",\"File Replication Service\",\"Directory Service\")\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| where EventLevelName in (\"Error\",\"Critical\")\n| extend Hour=format_datetime(TimeGenerated,'HH')\n| summarize Errors=count() by Hour, EventLog\n| order by Hour asc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Error Distribution by Hour of Day (All Sources)",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "barchart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "showLegend": true
              }
            }
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "overview-top-dcs",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog in (\"DFS Replication\",\"File Replication Service\",\"Directory Service\")\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| summarize\n    TotalEvents=count(),\n    DFSREvents=countif(EventLog==\"DFS Replication\"),\n    NTFRSEvents=countif(EventLog==\"File Replication Service\"),\n    DSEvents=countif(EventLog==\"Directory Service\"),\n    Errors=countif(EventLevelName in (\"Error\",\"Critical\")),\n    Warnings=countif(EventLevelName==\"Warning\"),\n    FirstSeen=min(TimeGenerated),\n    LastSeen=max(TimeGenerated)\n  by Computer\n| extend HealthStatus=case(\n    Errors > 100, \"Critical\",\n    Errors > 10, \"Degraded\",\n    Errors > 0, \"Warning\",\n    \"Healthy\"\n  )\n| order by Errors desc, TotalEvents desc\n| project Computer, HealthStatus, TotalEvents, Errors, Warnings, DFSREvents, NTFRSEvents, DSEvents, FirstSeen, LastSeen",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "All Domain Controllers - Event Summary",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "HealthStatus",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "colors",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "Critical",
                          "representation": "redBright",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "Degraded",
                          "representation": "orange",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "Warning",
                          "representation": "yellow",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "Healthy",
                          "representation": "green",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "blue",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "Errors",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "redBright"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "TotalEvents",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "blue"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "Warnings",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "yellow"
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "sortBy": [
                  {
                    "itemKey": "Errors",
                    "sortOrder": 2
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": 12,
      "name": "group-dfsr",
      "conditionalVisibility": {
        "parameterName": "Tab",
        "comparison": "isEqualTo",
        "value": "DFSR"
      },
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "## DFS Replication (DFSR) Health\n**Event Log Source:** `DFS Replication`\n\n**Critical Event IDs to watch:** 2213 (replication stopped — requires manual intervention), 4012 (partner exceeded max out-of-sync time), 5002 (DFSR service stopped), 6016 (sync failed), 4002 (init failed), 4004 (disk space).\n\n**Event 2213** is the most severe — it means DFSR has been halted and requires an authoritative restore (`BurFlags D4/D2`) or manual `wmic /namespace:\\\\root\\microsoftdfs path DfsrMachineConfig set StopReplicationOnAutoRecovery=FALSE` to recover.",
              "style": "warning"
            },
            "name": "dfsr-header"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "dfsr-kpis",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "let base = Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog == \"DFS Replication\"\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers});\nlet totalEvents = toscalar(base | count);\nlet dcCount = toscalar(base | summarize dcount(Computer));\nlet criticalCount = toscalar(base | where EventID in (2213, 4012, 5002, 6016, 4002, 4004) | count);\nlet stoppedCount = toscalar(base | where EventID in (2213, 5002) | count);\nlet syncErrorCount = toscalar(base | where EventID in (6016, 2104) | count);\nlet partnerTimeoutCount = toscalar(base | where EventID == 4012 | count);\nprint Metric=\"Total DFSR Events\", Value=totalEvents\n| union (print Metric=\"DCs with DFSR Events\", Value=dcCount)\n| union (print Metric=\"Critical Events\", Value=criticalCount)\n| union (print Metric=\"Service Stop Events\", Value=stoppedCount)\n| union (print Metric=\"Sync Errors (6016/2104)\", Value=syncErrorCount)\n| union (print Metric=\"Partner Timeout (4012)\", Value=partnerTimeoutCount)",
              "size": 4,
              "title": "DFSR Key Indicators",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "tiles",
              "tileSettings": {
                "showBorder": true,
                "titleContent": {
                  "columnMatch": "Metric",
                  "formatter": 1
                },
                "leftContent": {
                  "columnMatch": "Value",
                  "formatter": 12,
                  "formatOptions": {
                    "palette": "auto"
                  },
                  "numberFormat": {
                    "unit": 17,
                    "options": {
                      "style": "decimal",
                      "maximumFractionDigits": 0
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "dfsr-timeline",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog == \"DFS Replication\"\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| summarize Count=count() by bin(TimeGenerated, 1h), EventLevelName\n| order by TimeGenerated asc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "DFSR Event Volume Timeline (per Hour)",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "areachart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "showLegend": true,
                "seriesLabelSettings": [
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Error",
                    "color": "red"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Critical",
                    "color": "redBright"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Warning",
                    "color": "yellow"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Information",
                    "color": "blue"
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "dfsr-eventid-bar",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog == \"DFS Replication\"\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| summarize Count=count() by EventID\n| extend EventDescription=case(\n    EventID == 2213, \"2213: STOPPED — manual fixup required\",\n    EventID == 2212, \"2212: Multiple active DFSR instances\",\n    EventID == 2214, \"2214: Started after unexpected shutdown\",\n    EventID == 4012, \"4012: Partner exceeded max out-of-sync\",\n    EventID == 4004, \"4004: Out of disk space\",\n    EventID == 5002, \"5002: DFSR service STOPPED\",\n    EventID == 5004, \"5004: DFSR service started\",\n    EventID == 6016, \"6016: Could NOT sync replicated folder\",\n    EventID == 6018, \"6018: Sync recovered after error\",\n    EventID == 2104, \"2104: Error replicating a file\",\n    EventID == 4002, \"4002: FAILED to initialize\",\n    EventID == 5008, \"5008: File not replicated — staging full\",\n    EventID == 1202, \"1202: Replication group initialized\",\n    EventID == 1206, \"1206: Volume detected dirty\",\n    strcat(tostring(EventID), \": Other DFSR Event\")\n  )\n| order by Count desc\n| project EventDescription, Count",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "DFSR Events by Event ID",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "barchart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "showLegend": true
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "50"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "dfsr-dc-bar",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog == \"DFS Replication\"\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| where EventID in (2213, 4012, 5002, 6016, 4002, 4004, 2104, 5008, 2212, 1206)\n| summarize CriticalCount=count() by Computer\n| top 25 by CriticalCount desc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Top DCs by DFSR Critical/Warning Events",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "barchart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "showLegend": false
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "50"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "dfsr-critical-ref",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog == \"DFS Replication\"\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| where EventID in (2213, 4012, 5002, 6016, 4002, 4004, 2104, 5008, 2212, 2214, 1206, 5004, 1202, 6018)\n| summarize\n    Count=count(),\n    LastOccurrence=max(TimeGenerated),\n    AffectedDCs=dcount(Computer)\n  by EventID, EventLevelName\n| extend Severity=case(\n    EventID in (2213, 4012, 5002, 6016, 4002), \"Critical\",\n    EventID in (4004, 2104, 5008, 2212, 1206), \"Warning\",\n    EventID in (2214, 5004, 1202, 6018), \"Info\",\n    \"Other\"\n  )\n| extend Description=case(\n    EventID == 2213, \"DFSR STOPPED replication. Manual interventon required — BurFlags D4 authoritative or D2 non-authoritative restore of SYSVOL.\",\n    EventID == 4012, \"Partner DC exceeded maximum out-of-sync time. Check DFSR service and connectivity on the partner.\",\n    EventID == 5002, \"DFSR service STOPPED unexpectedly. Check service health and event 2213 for related stop reason.\",\n    EventID == 6016, \"DFSR could NOT synchronize the replicated folder. Investigate disk space, permissions, and staging area.\",\n    EventID == 4002, \"DFSR FAILED to initialize replication. Check staging area path and permissions.\",\n    EventID == 4004, \"DFSR ran out of DISK SPACE. Free space immediately to restore replication.\",\n    EventID == 2104, \"Error replicating a specific file. May indicate file locking, permissions, or corruption.\",\n    EventID == 5008, \"File NOT replicated — staging area full. Increase DFSR staging quota.\",\n    EventID == 2212, \"Multiple DFSR instances detected simultaneously. Investigate for duplicate services.\",\n    EventID == 1206, \"Volume dirty flag set. Indicates improper shutdown; DFSR may run CHKDSK.\",\n    EventID == 2214, \"DFSR auto-recovered from an unexpected shutdown.\",\n    EventID == 5004, \"DFSR service started normally.\",\n    EventID == 1202, \"Replication group initialized successfully.\",\n    EventID == 6018, \"Replicated folder re-synchronized after a previous sync error.\",\n    \"Other DFSR event.\"\n  )\n| order by Count desc\n| project EventID, Severity, Count, AffectedDCs, LastOccurrence, Description",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "DFSR Event ID Reference and Occurrence Count",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "Severity",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "colors",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "Critical",
                          "representation": "redBright",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "Warning",
                          "representation": "yellow",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "Info",
                          "representation": "green",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "blue",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "Count",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "redBright"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "AffectedDCs",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "orange"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "dfsr-service-state",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog == \"DFS Replication\"\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| where EventID in (5002, 5004, 2213, 2214)\n| extend EventType=case(\n    EventID == 5002, \"Service Stopped\",\n    EventID == 5004, \"Service Started\",\n    EventID == 2213, \"Replication HALTED\",\n    EventID == 2214, \"Replication Recovered\",\n    \"Other\"\n  )\n| summarize Count=count() by bin(TimeGenerated, 1h), EventType\n| order by TimeGenerated asc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "DFSR Service Start / Stop / Halt Events Timeline",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "linechart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "showLegend": true,
                "seriesLabelSettings": [
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Replication HALTED",
                    "color": "redBright"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Service Stopped",
                    "color": "red"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Service Started",
                    "color": "green"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Replication Recovered",
                    "color": "lime"
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "dfsr-recent-errors",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog == \"DFS Replication\"\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| where EventLevelName in (\"Error\",\"Critical\",\"Warning\")\n| extend Description=substring(RenderedDescription, 0, 300)\n| project TimeGenerated, Computer, EventID, EventLevelName, Description\n| order by TimeGenerated desc\n| take 500",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "DFSR Error and Warning Events - Detail",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "EventLevelName",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "colors",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "Critical",
                          "representation": "redBright",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "Error",
                          "representation": "red",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "Warning",
                          "representation": "yellow",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "blue",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "sortBy": [
                  {
                    "itemKey": "TimeGenerated",
                    "sortOrder": 2
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": 12,
      "name": "group-ntfrs",
      "conditionalVisibility": {
        "parameterName": "Tab",
        "comparison": "isEqualTo",
        "value": "NTFRS"
      },
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "## File Replication Service (NTFRS) Health\n**Event Log Source:** `File Replication Service`\n\nNTFRS is the legacy SYSVOL replication engine (pre-DFSR). **Critical Event IDs:** 13508 (partner replication failing), 13520 (journal wrap — D2 BurFlags needed), 13552 (SYSVOL replication failing), 13555 (serious service problems), 13568 (auto journal wrap fix applied), 13572 (SYSVOL not ready).\n\n**Event 13520 / 13568** (journal wrap) requires setting `BurFlags = D2` for non-authoritative SYSVOL restore. **Event 13552** combined with 13572 means the DC's SYSVOL is not replicating and the DC should not be trusted for Group Policy.",
              "style": "warning"
            },
            "name": "ntfrs-header"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "ntfrs-kpis",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "let base = Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog == \"File Replication Service\"\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers});\nlet totalEvents = toscalar(base | count);\nlet dcCount = toscalar(base | summarize dcount(Computer));\nlet criticalCount = toscalar(base | where EventID in (13508, 13520, 13552, 13555, 13568, 13572) | count);\nlet journalWrapCount = toscalar(base | where EventID in (13520, 13568) | count);\nlet sysvolFailureCount = toscalar(base | where EventID in (13552, 13572) | count);\nlet partnerIssueCount = toscalar(base | where EventID == 13508 | count);\nprint Metric=\"Total NTFRS Events\", Value=totalEvents\n| union (print Metric=\"DCs with NTFRS Events\", Value=dcCount)\n| union (print Metric=\"Critical Events\", Value=criticalCount)\n| union (print Metric=\"Journal Wrap Errors\", Value=journalWrapCount)\n| union (print Metric=\"SYSVOL Failures\", Value=sysvolFailureCount)\n| union (print Metric=\"Partner Issues (13508)\", Value=partnerIssueCount)",
              "size": 4,
              "title": "NTFRS Key Indicators",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "tiles",
              "tileSettings": {
                "showBorder": true,
                "titleContent": {
                  "columnMatch": "Metric",
                  "formatter": 1
                },
                "leftContent": {
                  "columnMatch": "Value",
                  "formatter": 12,
                  "formatOptions": {
                    "palette": "auto"
                  },
                  "numberFormat": {
                    "unit": 17,
                    "options": {
                      "style": "decimal",
                      "maximumFractionDigits": 0
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "ntfrs-timeline",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog == \"File Replication Service\"\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| summarize Count=count() by bin(TimeGenerated, 1h), EventLevelName\n| order by TimeGenerated asc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "NTFRS Event Volume Timeline (per Hour)",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "areachart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "showLegend": true,
                "seriesLabelSettings": [
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Error",
                    "color": "red"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Warning",
                    "color": "yellow"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Information",
                    "color": "blue"
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "ntfrs-eventid-bar",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog == \"File Replication Service\"\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| summarize Count=count() by EventID\n| extend EventDescription=case(\n    EventID == 13508, \"13508: Trouble enabling replication from partner\",\n    EventID == 13509, \"13509: Replication enabled with partner\",\n    EventID == 13516, \"13516: No longer preventing DC promotion\",\n    EventID == 13520, \"13520: JRNL_WRAP_ERROR — D2 BurFlags required\",\n    EventID == 13522, \"13522: FRS not responding — timeout\",\n    EventID == 13536, \"13536: Cannot resolve partner DNS name\",\n    EventID == 13548, \"13548: FRS cannot be contacted\",\n    EventID == 13552, \"13552: SYSVOL replication FAILING\",\n    EventID == 13553, \"13553: Connection established with partner\",\n    EventID == 13555, \"13555: Serious FRS service problems\",\n    EventID == 13566, \"13566: BurFlags restore mode detected\",\n    EventID == 13568, \"13568: Journal wrap — auto D2 BurFlags set\",\n    EventID == 13572, \"13572: DC SYSVOL NOT READY\",\n    EventID == 13573, \"13573: SYSVOL ready / sharing started\",\n    strcat(tostring(EventID), \": Other NTFRS Event\")\n  )\n| order by Count desc\n| project EventDescription, Count",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "NTFRS Events by Event ID",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "barchart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "showLegend": false
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "50"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "ntfrs-jrnl-dc",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog == \"File Replication Service\"\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| where EventID in (13520, 13568)\n| summarize JournalWrapEvents=count(), LastOccurrence=max(TimeGenerated) by Computer\n| order by JournalWrapEvents desc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Journal Wrap Errors (13520 / 13568) by DC",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "barchart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "showLegend": false
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "50"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "ntfrs-sysvol-fail-dc",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog == \"File Replication Service\"\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| where EventID in (13552, 13572)\n| summarize SYSVOLFailures=count(), LastOccurrence=max(TimeGenerated) by Computer, EventID\n| extend EventType=iff(EventID==13552, \"SYSVOL Replication Failing\", \"SYSVOL Not Ready\")\n| order by SYSVOLFailures desc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "SYSVOL Failures (13552 / 13572) by DC",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "barchart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "showLegend": true
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "50"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "ntfrs-partner-connectivity",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog == \"File Replication Service\"\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| where EventID in (13508, 13548, 13553)\n| summarize Count=count() by bin(TimeGenerated, 1h), EventID\n| extend EventType=case(\n    EventID == 13508, \"Partner Unreachable (13508)\",\n    EventID == 13548, \"FRS Cannot Contact (13548)\",\n    EventID == 13553, \"Partner Connected (13553)\",\n    \"Other\"\n  )\n| project TimeGenerated, EventType, Count\n| order by TimeGenerated asc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "NTFRS Partner Connectivity Timeline (13508 failing / 13553 established)",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "linechart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "showLegend": true,
                "seriesLabelSettings": [
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Partner Unreachable (13508)",
                    "color": "red"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "FRS Cannot Contact (13548)",
                    "color": "orange"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Partner Connected (13553)",
                    "color": "green"
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "50"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "ntfrs-critical-ref",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog == \"File Replication Service\"\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| where EventID in (13508, 13509, 13516, 13520, 13522, 13536, 13548, 13552, 13553, 13555, 13566, 13568, 13572, 13573)\n| summarize\n    Count=count(),\n    LastOccurrence=max(TimeGenerated),\n    AffectedDCs=dcount(Computer)\n  by EventID\n| extend Severity=case(\n    EventID in (13508, 13520, 13522, 13548, 13552, 13555, 13572), \"Critical\",\n    EventID in (13536, 13568), \"Warning\",\n    EventID in (13509, 13516, 13553, 13566, 13573), \"Info\",\n    \"Other\"\n  )\n| extend Description=case(\n    EventID == 13508, \"FRS is having trouble enabling replication from the partner. Check network, DNS, and FRS service on partner.\",\n    EventID == 13509, \"FRS has enabled replication from the partner — connectivity restored.\",\n    EventID == 13516, \"FRS is no longer preventing the computer from becoming a domain controller.\",\n    EventID == 13520, \"Replica set in JRNL_WRAP_ERROR — set BurFlags=D2 in registry under HKLM\\\\System\\\\CurrentControlSet\\\\Services\\\\NtFrs\\\\Parameters\\\\Cumulative Replica Sets.\",\n    EventID == 13522, \"FRS is not responding after timeout — FRS service may be hung. Restart FRS service.\",\n    EventID == 13536, \"FRS cannot resolve DNS name of replication partner — fix DNS resolution.\",\n    EventID == 13548, \"FRS cannot be contacted — firewall, network, or service issue on partner DC.\",\n    EventID == 13552, \"FRS is FAILING to replicate SYSVOL — DC's SYSVOL is inconsistent. Check 13568 and journal wrap.\",\n    EventID == 13553, \"FRS successfully established connection with replication partner.\",\n    EventID == 13555, \"Serious FRS service problems — FRS may stop replicating. Check Application logs and KB article.\",\n    EventID == 13566, \"FRS detected NTFRS in BurFlags restore mode — monitoring BurFlags progress.\",\n    EventID == 13568, \"FRS automatically set D2 BurFlags due to journal wrap. SYSVOL will sync from upstream partner.\",\n    EventID == 13572, \"DC SYSVOL is NOT READY — SYSVOL not shared, GP not applied from this DC.\",\n    EventID == 13573, \"SYSVOL is now READY and being shared — replication healthy.\",\n    \"Other event.\"\n  )\n| order by Count desc\n| project EventID, Severity, Count, AffectedDCs, LastOccurrence, Description",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "NTFRS Event ID Reference and Occurrence Count",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "Severity",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "colors",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "Critical",
                          "representation": "redBright",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "Warning",
                          "representation": "yellow",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "Info",
                          "representation": "green",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "blue",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "Count",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "redBright"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "AffectedDCs",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "orange"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "ntfrs-recent-errors",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog == \"File Replication Service\"\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| where EventLevelName in (\"Error\",\"Critical\",\"Warning\")\n| extend Description=substring(RenderedDescription, 0, 300)\n| project TimeGenerated, Computer, EventID, EventLevelName, Description\n| order by TimeGenerated desc\n| take 500",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "NTFRS Error and Warning Events - Detail",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "EventLevelName",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "colors",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "Error",
                          "representation": "red",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "Critical",
                          "representation": "redBright",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "Warning",
                          "representation": "yellow",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "blue",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": 12,
      "name": "group-ds",
      "conditionalVisibility": {
        "parameterName": "Tab",
        "comparison": "isEqualTo",
        "value": "DS"
      },
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "## Active Directory Directory Service Health\n**Event Log Source:** `Directory Service`\n\n**Critical Event IDs:** 1311 (KCC replication errors), 1388 (inbound replication DISABLED), 1925 (replication link failed), 2042 (too long since replication), 1866 (KCC spanning tree failure), 5805 (session setup failed), 1645 (no RID pools).\n\n**Event 2042** means replication has not occurred for longer than the tombstone lifetime — this DC is **ISOLATED** and should be demoted/repromoted or restored from backup. **Event 1388** means replication has been DISABLED and ADSI Edit may be required to re-enable it.",
              "style": "warning"
            },
            "name": "ds-header"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "ds-kpis",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "let base = Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog == \"Directory Service\"\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers});\nlet totalEvents = toscalar(base | count);\nlet dcCount = toscalar(base | summarize dcount(Computer));\nlet replicationFailureCount = toscalar(base | where EventID in (1311, 1388, 1925, 2042) | count);\nlet kccErrorCount = toscalar(base | where EventID in (1311, 1866) | count);\nlet dnsFailureCount = toscalar(base | where EventID in (2087, 2088) | count);\nlet allErrorCount = toscalar(base | where EventLevelName in (\"Error\",\"Critical\") | count);\nprint Metric=\"Total DS Events\", Value=totalEvents\n| union (print Metric=\"DCs Reporting\", Value=dcCount)\n| union (print Metric=\"Replication Failures\", Value=replicationFailureCount)\n| union (print Metric=\"KCC Errors\", Value=kccErrorCount)\n| union (print Metric=\"DNS Failures\", Value=dnsFailureCount)\n| union (print Metric=\"All Errors / Critical\", Value=allErrorCount)",
              "size": 4,
              "title": "Directory Service Key Indicators",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "tiles",
              "tileSettings": {
                "showBorder": true,
                "titleContent": {
                  "columnMatch": "Metric",
                  "formatter": 1
                },
                "leftContent": {
                  "columnMatch": "Value",
                  "formatter": 12,
                  "formatOptions": {
                    "palette": "auto"
                  },
                  "numberFormat": {
                    "unit": 17,
                    "options": {
                      "style": "decimal",
                      "maximumFractionDigits": 0
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "ds-timeline",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog == \"Directory Service\"\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| summarize Count=count() by bin(TimeGenerated, 1h), EventLevelName\n| order by TimeGenerated asc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Directory Service Event Volume Timeline (per Hour)",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "areachart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "showLegend": true,
                "seriesLabelSettings": [
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Error",
                    "color": "red"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Critical",
                    "color": "redBright"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Warning",
                    "color": "yellow"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Information",
                    "color": "blue"
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "ds-replid-bar",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog == \"Directory Service\"\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| where EventID in (1311, 1388, 1925, 1926, 2042, 2087, 2088, 1864, 1866, 1645, 5805, 1173, 1168, 1655)\n| summarize Count=count() by EventID\n| extend EventDescription=case(\n    EventID == 1311, \"1311: KCC replication errors detected\",\n    EventID == 1388, \"1388: Inbound replication DISABLED\",\n    EventID == 1925, \"1925: Replication link establishment FAILED\",\n    EventID == 1926, \"1926: Read-only partition link failed\",\n    EventID == 2042, \"2042: Too long since last replication — ISOLATED DC\",\n    EventID == 2087, \"2087: DNS lookup failure — replication failed\",\n    EventID == 2088, \"2088: DNS failure (replication still succeeded)\",\n    EventID == 1864, \"1864: Replication warning threshold reached\",\n    EventID == 1866, \"1866: KCC cannot build spanning tree\",\n    EventID == 1645, \"1645: No RID pools available\",\n    EventID == 5805, \"5805: Session setup failed\",\n    EventID == 1173, \"1173: Internal AD transaction error\",\n    EventID == 1168, \"1168: Unexpected internal exception\",\n    EventID == 1655, \"1655: Global catalog contact failed\",\n    strcat(tostring(EventID), \": Other DS Event\")\n  )\n| order by Count desc\n| project EventDescription, Count",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "AD Replication & DS Events by Event ID",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "barchart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "showLegend": false
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "50"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "ds-dc-bar",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog == \"Directory Service\"\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| where EventID in (1311, 1388, 1925, 1926, 2042, 1864, 1866, 1645, 5805, 1173, 1168, 2087)\n| summarize CriticalCount=count() by Computer\n| top 25 by CriticalCount desc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Top DCs by AD Replication / DS Critical Events",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "barchart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "showLegend": false
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "50"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "ds-dns-analysis",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog == \"Directory Service\"\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| where EventID in (2087, 2088)\n| summarize\n    TotalDNSEvents=count(),\n    DNS_Fail_Repl_Failed=countif(EventID==2087),\n    DNS_Fail_Repl_OK=countif(EventID==2088),\n    LastOccurrence=max(TimeGenerated)\n  by Computer\n| extend DNSStatus=case(\n    DNS_Fail_Repl_Failed > 0 and DNS_Fail_Repl_OK == 0, \"DNS Failing — Replication Also Failing\",\n    DNS_Fail_Repl_Failed > 0, \"DNS Failing — But Replication Recovered\",\n    \"DNS Resolution OK (2088 only)\"\n  )\n| order by DNS_Fail_Repl_Failed desc\n| project Computer, DNSStatus, DNS_Fail_Repl_Failed, DNS_Fail_Repl_OK, LastOccurrence",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "DNS Lookup Failure Analysis (2087 / 2088) by DC",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "DNSStatus",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "colors",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "Failing — Replication Also Failing",
                          "representation": "redBright",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "Failing — But Replication Recovered",
                          "representation": "yellow",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "green",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "DNS_Fail_Repl_Failed",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "redBright"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "50"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "ds-repl-partner",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog == \"Directory Service\"\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| where EventID in (1311, 1388, 1925, 2042)\n| summarize\n    ReplicationErrors=count(),\n    LastError=max(TimeGenerated),\n    FirstError=min(TimeGenerated),\n    DistinctEventIDs=dcount(EventID),\n    Event1311=countif(EventID==1311),\n    Event1388=countif(EventID==1388),\n    Event1925=countif(EventID==1925),\n    Event2042=countif(EventID==2042)\n  by Computer\n| extend HoursWithoutRepl=datetime_diff(\"hour\", now(), LastError)\n| order by ReplicationErrors desc\n| project Computer, ReplicationErrors, Event2042, Event1388, Event1925, Event1311, DistinctEventIDs, FirstError, LastError",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "AD Replication Failure Detail by DC",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "ReplicationErrors",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "redBright"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "Event2042",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "red"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "Event1388",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "orange"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "50"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "ds-critical-ref",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog == \"Directory Service\"\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| where EventID in (1311, 1388, 1925, 1926, 2042, 2087, 2088, 1864, 1866, 1645, 5805, 1173, 1168, 1655)\n| summarize\n    Count=count(),\n    LastOccurrence=max(TimeGenerated),\n    AffectedDCs=dcount(Computer)\n  by EventID\n| extend Severity=case(\n    EventID in (1311, 1388, 2042, 1645, 1866, 1925, 5805, 1173, 1168), \"Critical\",\n    EventID in (2087, 1864, 1926, 2088, 1655), \"Warning\",\n    \"Other\"\n  )\n| extend Description=case(\n    EventID == 1311, \"KCC has detected that replication attempts have been unsuccessful. Check AD Sites & Services and repadmin /showrepl.\",\n    EventID == 1388, \"Inbound replication of a directory partition has been DISABLED. Run repadmin /options to re-enable.\",\n    EventID == 1925, \"Attempt to establish a replication link FAILED. Check network connectivity and DNS between DCs.\",\n    EventID == 1926, \"Attempt to establish a replication link to read-only partition failed.\",\n    EventID == 2042, \"Replication has NOT occurred for longer than tombstone lifetime — DC is ISOLATED. Consider demotion and repromote.\",\n    EventID == 2087, \"DNS lookup failure caused REPLICATION TO FAIL. Fix DNS resolution for partner DCs.\",\n    EventID == 2088, \"DNS lookup failed but replication succeeded via IP fallback. Fix DNS anyway.\",\n    EventID == 1864, \"Replication has not occurred within warning threshold. Investigate replication topology.\",\n    EventID == 1866, \"KCC could not build a spanning tree for directory replication. Check AD Sites & Services.\",\n    EventID == 1645, \"No RID pools available — new objects cannot be created. Contact RID master DC.\",\n    EventID == 5805, \"Session setup failed — check secure channel and machine account password.\",\n    EventID == 1173, \"Internal Active Directory transaction error — check disk health and AD database integrity.\",\n    EventID == 1168, \"Unexpected internal exception in AD DS — run dcdiag and check for database corruption.\",\n    EventID == 1655, \"Attempt to contact global catalog FAILED — GC needed for logons and UPN resolution.\",\n    \"Other DS event.\"\n  )\n| order by Count desc\n| project EventID, Severity, Count, AffectedDCs, LastOccurrence, Description",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Directory Service Event ID Reference and Counts",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "Severity",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "colors",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "Critical",
                          "representation": "redBright",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "Warning",
                          "representation": "yellow",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "blue",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "Count",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "redBright"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "AffectedDCs",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "orange"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "ds-recent-errors",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog == \"Directory Service\"\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| where EventLevelName in (\"Error\",\"Critical\",\"Warning\")\n| extend Description=substring(RenderedDescription, 0, 300)\n| project TimeGenerated, Computer, EventID, EventLevelName, Description\n| order by TimeGenerated desc\n| take 500",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Directory Service Error and Warning Events - Detail",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "EventLevelName",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "colors",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "Error",
                          "representation": "red",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "Critical",
                          "representation": "redBright",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "Warning",
                          "representation": "yellow",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "blue",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": 12,
      "name": "group-socsecurity",
      "conditionalVisibility": {
        "parameterName": "Tab",
        "comparison": "isEqualTo",
        "value": "SOCSecurity"
      },
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "## Security and MDE Operations\nThis tab is focused on sysadmin and security operations for domain controllers using security telemetry, MDE advanced hunting data, and Arc-connected heartbeat signals. It emphasizes your high-priority replication and service event IDs: **4012, 2213, 5002, 5008, 4202, 4204, 4412, 4414, 1206, 1202**.",
              "style": "error"
            },
            "name": "socsecurity-header"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "socsecurity-kpis",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "let focusIds = dynamic([4012,2213,5002,5008,4202,4204,4412,4414,1206,1202]);\nlet focusEvents = Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog in (\"DFS Replication\",\"File Replication Service\",\"Directory Service\")\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| where EventID in (4012,2213,5002,5008,4202,4204,4412,4414,1206,1202);\nlet secEvents = union isfuzzy=true\n  (SecurityEvent\n  | where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n  | where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n  | where EventID in (4012,2213,5002,5008,4202,4204,4412,4414,1206,1202)\n  | project TimeGenerated, Computer, EventID),\n  (datatable(TimeGenerated:datetime, Computer:string, EventID:int)[]);\nlet mdeNetwork = union isfuzzy=true\n  (DeviceNetworkEvents\n  | where Timestamp {TimeRange}\n  | where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or DeviceName in~ ({Computers})\n  | project TimeGenerated=Timestamp, Computer=DeviceName),\n  (datatable(TimeGenerated:datetime, Computer:string)[]);\nlet mdeAuth = union isfuzzy=true\n  (DeviceLogonEvents\n  | where Timestamp {TimeRange}\n  | where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or DeviceName in~ ({Computers})\n  | project TimeGenerated=Timestamp, Computer=DeviceName),\n  (datatable(TimeGenerated:datetime, Computer:string)[]);\nlet arcHeartbeat = union isfuzzy=true\n  (Heartbeat\n  | where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n  | where ResourceType has \"microsoft.hybridcompute/machines\"\n  | where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n  | project TimeGenerated, Computer),\n  (datatable(TimeGenerated:datetime, Computer:string)[]);\nlet focusCount = toscalar(focusEvents | count);\nlet securityCount = toscalar(secEvents | count);\nlet uniqueDCs = toscalar(focusEvents | summarize dcount(Computer));\nlet mdeNetworkCount = toscalar(mdeNetwork | count);\nlet mdeLogonCount = toscalar(mdeAuth | count);\nlet arcHeartbeatCount = toscalar(arcHeartbeat | count);\nprint Metric=\"Focus ID Events (Event)\", Value=focusCount\n| union (print Metric=\"Focus ID Events (SecurityEvent)\", Value=securityCount)\n| union (print Metric=\"DCs with Focus IDs\", Value=uniqueDCs)\n| union (print Metric=\"MDE Network Events\", Value=mdeNetworkCount)\n| union (print Metric=\"MDE Logon Events\", Value=mdeLogonCount)\n| union (print Metric=\"Arc Heartbeat Records\", Value=arcHeartbeatCount)",
              "size": 4,
              "title": "Security Operations KPIs",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "tiles",
              "tileSettings": {
                "showBorder": true,
                "titleContent": {
                  "columnMatch": "Metric",
                  "formatter": 1
                },
                "leftContent": {
                  "columnMatch": "Value",
                  "formatter": 12,
                  "formatOptions": {
                    "palette": "auto"
                  },
                  "numberFormat": {
                    "unit": 17,
                    "options": {
                      "style": "decimal",
                      "maximumFractionDigits": 0
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "socsecurity-focusid-timeline",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "let focus = dynamic([4012,2213,5002,5008,4202,4204,4412,4414,1206,1202]);\nlet fromEvent = Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventID in (4012,2213,5002,5008,4202,4204,4412,4414,1206,1202)\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| project TimeGenerated, Computer, EventID, Source=\"Event\";\nlet fromSecurity = union isfuzzy=true\n  (SecurityEvent\n  | where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n  | where EventID in (4012,2213,5002,5008,4202,4204,4412,4414,1206,1202)\n  | where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n  | project TimeGenerated, Computer, EventID, Source=\"SecurityEvent\"),\n  (datatable(TimeGenerated:datetime, Computer:string, EventID:int, Source:string)[]);\nunion fromEvent, fromSecurity\n| summarize Count=count() by bin(TimeGenerated, 1h), Source\n| order by TimeGenerated asc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Focus Event ID Volume Over Time (Event plus SecurityEvent)",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "areachart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "showLegend": true,
                "seriesLabelSettings": [
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Event",
                    "color": "orange"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "SecurityEvent",
                    "color": "red"
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "socsecurity-focusid-by-dc",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "let focus = dynamic([4012,2213,5002,5008,4202,4204,4412,4414,1206,1202]);\nlet evt = Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventID in (4012,2213,5002,5008,4202,4204,4412,4414,1206,1202)\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| project TimeGenerated, Computer, EventID, SourceLog=EventLog;\nlet sec = union isfuzzy=true\n  (SecurityEvent\n  | where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n  | where EventID in (4012,2213,5002,5008,4202,4204,4412,4414,1206,1202)\n  | where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n  | project TimeGenerated, Computer, EventID, SourceLog=\"SecurityEvent\"),\n  (datatable(TimeGenerated:datetime, Computer:string, EventID:int, SourceLog:string)[]);\nunion evt, sec\n| summarize Count=count(), FirstSeen=min(TimeGenerated), LastSeen=max(TimeGenerated), Sources=make_set(SourceLog) by Computer, EventID\n| extend SourceCount=array_length(Sources)\n| order by Count desc\n| project Computer, EventID, Count, SourceCount, FirstSeen, LastSeen, Sources",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Focus Event IDs by DC and Source",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "Count",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "redBright"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "SourceCount",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "orange"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "50"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "socsecurity-securityevent-logon",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "union isfuzzy=true\n  (SecurityEvent\n  | where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n  | where EventID in (4624,4625,4672,4768,4769,4771,4776)\n  | where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n  | summarize Count=count(), Accounts=dcount(Account), LastSeen=max(TimeGenerated) by Computer, EventID),\n  (datatable(Computer:string, EventID:int, Count:long, Accounts:long, LastSeen:datetime)[])\n| extend EventLabel=case(\n    EventID == 4624, \"Successful Logon (4624)\",\n    EventID == 4625, \"Failed Logon (4625)\",\n    EventID == 4672, \"Special Privileges Assigned (4672)\",\n    EventID == 4768, \"Kerberos TGT Request (4768)\",\n    EventID == 4769, \"Kerberos Service Ticket (4769)\",\n    EventID == 4771, \"Kerberos Pre-auth Failed (4771)\",\n    EventID == 4776, \"NTLM Authentication (4776)\",\n    tostring(EventID)\n  )\n| order by Count desc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "SecurityEvent Authentication Activity by DC",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "Count",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "yellowRed"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "Accounts",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "blueGreen"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "50"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "socsecurity-mde-network-trend",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "union isfuzzy=true\n  (DeviceNetworkEvents\n  | where Timestamp {TimeRange}\n  | where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or DeviceName in~ ({Computers})\n  | summarize Count=count() by bin(Timestamp, 1h), ActionType\n  | project TimeGenerated=Timestamp, Count, ActionType),\n  (datatable(TimeGenerated:datetime, Count:long, ActionType:string)[])\n| order by TimeGenerated asc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "MDE Network Event Trend by Action Type",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "linechart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "showLegend": true
              }
            }
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "socsecurity-mde-ops-summary",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "let netRaw = union isfuzzy=true\n  (DeviceNetworkEvents\n  | where Timestamp {TimeRange}\n  | where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or DeviceName in~ ({Computers})\n  | project TimeGenerated=Timestamp, Computer=DeviceName, Action=tostring(ActionType), RemoteIP=tostring(RemoteIP), RemoteUrl=tostring(RemoteUrl), RemotePort=tostring(RemotePort), Protocol=tostring(Protocol)),\n  (datatable(TimeGenerated:datetime, Computer:string, Action:string, RemoteIP:string, RemoteUrl:string, RemotePort:string, Protocol:string)[]);\nlet net = netRaw\n| summarize Events=count(), UniqueActions=dcount(Action), UniqueRemoteIPs=dcountif(RemoteIP, isnotempty(RemoteIP)), UniqueRemoteUrls=dcountif(RemoteUrl, isnotempty(RemoteUrl)), UniqueRemotePorts=dcountif(RemotePort, isnotempty(RemotePort)), Protocols=make_set_if(Protocol, isnotempty(Protocol), 8), LastSeen=max(TimeGenerated) by Computer\n| extend Signal=\"Network\";\nlet proc = union isfuzzy=true\n  (DeviceProcessEvents\n  | where Timestamp {TimeRange}\n  | where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or DeviceName in~ ({Computers})\n  | project TimeGenerated=Timestamp, Computer=DeviceName, Action=tostring(ActionType)),\n  (datatable(TimeGenerated:datetime, Computer:string, Action:string)[])\n| summarize Events=count(), UniqueActions=dcount(Action), LastSeen=max(TimeGenerated) by Computer\n| extend Signal=\"Process\", UniqueRemoteIPs=long(null), UniqueRemoteUrls=long(null), UniqueRemotePorts=long(null), Protocols=dynamic(null);\nlet logon = union isfuzzy=true\n  (DeviceLogonEvents\n  | where Timestamp {TimeRange}\n  | where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or DeviceName in~ ({Computers})\n  | project TimeGenerated=Timestamp, Computer=DeviceName, Action=tostring(ActionType)),\n  (datatable(TimeGenerated:datetime, Computer:string, Action:string)[])\n| summarize Events=count(), UniqueActions=dcount(Action), LastSeen=max(TimeGenerated) by Computer\n| extend Signal=\"Logon\", UniqueRemoteIPs=long(null), UniqueRemoteUrls=long(null), UniqueRemotePorts=long(null), Protocols=dynamic(null);\nunion net, proc, logon\n| order by Events desc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "MDE Operational Signals by DC (Network, Process, Logon)",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "Events",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "yellowRed"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "UniqueActions",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "blue"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "100"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "socsecurity-arc-heartbeat",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "union isfuzzy=true\n  (Heartbeat\n  | where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n  | where ResourceType has \"microsoft.hybridcompute/machines\"\n  | where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n  | summarize Heartbeats=count(), LastHeartbeat=max(TimeGenerated), FirstHeartbeat=min(TimeGenerated) by Computer, OSType, ResourceId),\n  (datatable(Computer:string, Heartbeats:long, LastHeartbeat:datetime, FirstHeartbeat:datetime, OSType:string, ResourceId:string)[])\n| extend ArcStatus=case(\n    Heartbeats == 0, \"No Arc Heartbeat\",\n    datetime_diff(\"minute\", now(), LastHeartbeat) > 60, \"Arc Stale\",\n    \"Arc Active\"\n  )\n| order by Heartbeats desc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Arc Connected DC Heartbeat Coverage",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "ArcStatus",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "colors",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "No Arc",
                          "representation": "redBright",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "Stale",
                          "representation": "yellow",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "green",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "Heartbeats",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "blue"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": 12,
      "name": "group-critical",
      "conditionalVisibility": {
        "parameterName": "Tab",
        "comparison": "isEqualTo",
        "value": "Critical"
      },
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "## Cross-Source Critical Events\nThis tab consolidates **Error and Critical** severity events across all three log sources into a single operational view. DCs appearing in the **Multi-Source Impact** table have problems in 2 or more replication subsystems and are the highest priority for remediation.",
              "style": "error"
            },
            "name": "critical-header"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "critical-timeline",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog in (\"DFS Replication\",\"File Replication Service\",\"Directory Service\")\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| where EventLevelName in (\"Error\",\"Critical\")\n| summarize Count=count() by bin(TimeGenerated, 1h), EventLog\n| order by TimeGenerated asc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Error and Critical Events Timeline - All Sources",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "areachart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "showLegend": true,
                "seriesLabelSettings": [
                  {
                    "seriesName": "DFS Replication",
                    "color": "red"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "File Replication Service",
                    "color": "orange"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Directory Service",
                    "color": "purple"
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "critical-by-dc-source",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog in (\"DFS Replication\",\"File Replication Service\",\"Directory Service\")\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| where EventLevelName in (\"Error\",\"Critical\")\n| summarize\n    TotalErrors=count(),\n    DFSRErrors=countif(EventLog==\"DFS Replication\"),\n    NTFRSErrors=countif(EventLog==\"File Replication Service\"),\n    DSErrors=countif(EventLog==\"Directory Service\"),\n    FirstError=min(TimeGenerated),\n    LastError=max(TimeGenerated)\n  by Computer\n| extend SourcesAffected=(iff(DFSRErrors>0, 1, 0) + iff(NTFRSErrors>0, 1, 0) + iff(DSErrors>0, 1, 0))\n| extend RiskLevel=case(\n    SourcesAffected >= 3, \"ALL 3 SOURCES FAILING\",\n    SourcesAffected == 2, \"2 Sources Failing\",\n    SourcesAffected == 1, \"1 Source\",\n    \"No Errors\"\n  )\n| order by TotalErrors desc\n| project Computer, RiskLevel, TotalErrors, DFSRErrors, NTFRSErrors, DSErrors, SourcesAffected, FirstError, LastError",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Error Distribution by DC - All Sources Combined",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "RiskLevel",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "colors",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "ALL 3",
                          "representation": "redBright",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "2 Sources",
                          "representation": "orange",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "1 Source",
                          "representation": "yellow",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "green",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "TotalErrors",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "redBright"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "DFSRErrors",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "red"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "NTFRSErrors",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "orange"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "DSErrors",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "purple"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "SourcesAffected",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "max": 3,
                      "palette": "redBright"
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "sortBy": [
                  {
                    "itemKey": "TotalErrors",
                    "sortOrder": 2
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "critical-multi-source",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog in (\"DFS Replication\",\"File Replication Service\",\"Directory Service\")\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| where EventLevelName in (\"Error\",\"Critical\")\n| summarize Sources=make_set(EventLog), ErrorCount=count() by Computer\n| where array_length(Sources) >= 2\n| extend SourceList=tostring(Sources)\n| order by array_length(Sources) desc, ErrorCount desc\n| project Computer, SourceList, ErrorCount",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Multi-Source Impact - DCs with Errors in 2 or More Log Sources",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "ErrorCount",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "redBright"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "50"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "critical-top-eventids",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog in (\"DFS Replication\",\"File Replication Service\",\"Directory Service\")\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| where EventLevelName in (\"Error\",\"Critical\")\n| summarize Count=count(), AffectedDCs=dcount(Computer) by EventID, EventLog\n| order by Count desc\n| take 25",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Top 25 Critical Event IDs",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "Count",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "redBright"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "AffectedDCs",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "orange"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "50"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "critical-stacked-bar",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog in (\"DFS Replication\",\"File Replication Service\",\"Directory Service\")\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| where EventLevelName in (\"Error\",\"Critical\")\n| summarize\n    DFSRErrors=countif(EventLog==\"DFS Replication\"),\n    NTFRSErrors=countif(EventLog==\"File Replication Service\"),\n    DSErrors=countif(EventLog==\"Directory Service\")\n  by Computer\n| top 25 by (DFSRErrors + NTFRSErrors + DSErrors) desc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Top 25 DCs by Error Count - Stacked by Source",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "barchart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "showLegend": true,
                "seriesLabelSettings": [
                  {
                    "seriesName": "DFSRErrors",
                    "label": "DFSR",
                    "color": "red"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "NTFRSErrors",
                    "label": "NTFRS",
                    "color": "orange"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "DSErrors",
                    "label": "Directory Service",
                    "color": "purple"
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "critical-full-table",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog in (\"DFS Replication\",\"File Replication Service\",\"Directory Service\")\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| where EventLevelName in (\"Error\",\"Critical\")\n| extend Description=substring(RenderedDescription, 0, 400)\n| project TimeGenerated, Computer, EventLog, EventID, EventLevelName, Description\n| order by TimeGenerated desc\n| take 1000",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "All Critical and Error Events - Full Detail (Latest 1000)",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "EventLevelName",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "colors",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "Critical",
                          "representation": "redBright",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "Error",
                          "representation": "red",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "blue",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "EventLog",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "colors",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "DFS Replication",
                          "representation": "red",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "File Replication Service",
                          "representation": "orange",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "Directory Service",
                          "representation": "purple",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "blue",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "sortBy": [
                  {
                    "itemKey": "TimeGenerated",
                    "sortOrder": 2
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": 12,
      "name": "group-dcmatrix",
      "conditionalVisibility": {
        "parameterName": "Tab",
        "comparison": "isEqualTo",
        "value": "DCMatrix"
      },
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "## DC Health Matrix\nThis tab provides a per-DC health scorecard across all three replication subsystems. The **Overall Health** column aggregates DFSR, NTFRS, and Directory Service status into a single signal. Use this view for daily SOC review and as a starting point for targeted investigation.\n\n| Status | Meaning |\n|---|---|\n| Critical | One or more critical event IDs observed (e.g., 2213, 13552, 2042) |\n| Degraded | Errors or warnings observed but no critical-tier event IDs |\n| Active | Events logging normally, no errors |\n| No Data | No events received — check DCR and agent health |",
              "style": "info"
            },
            "name": "dcmatrix-header"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "dcmatrix-scorecard",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog in (\"DFS Replication\",\"File Replication Service\",\"Directory Service\")\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| summarize\n    TotalEvents=count(),\n    DFSRTotal=countif(EventLog==\"DFS Replication\"),\n    DFSRErrors=countif(EventLog==\"DFS Replication\" and EventLevelName in (\"Error\",\"Critical\")),\n    DFSRCritical=countif(EventLog==\"DFS Replication\" and EventID in (2213, 4012, 5002, 6016, 4002)),\n    NTFRSTotal=countif(EventLog==\"File Replication Service\"),\n    NTFRSErrors=countif(EventLog==\"File Replication Service\" and EventLevelName in (\"Error\",\"Critical\")),\n    NTFRSCritical=countif(EventLog==\"File Replication Service\" and EventID in (13508, 13520, 13552, 13555, 13568, 13572)),\n    DSTotal=countif(EventLog==\"Directory Service\"),\n    DSErrors=countif(EventLog==\"Directory Service\" and EventLevelName in (\"Error\",\"Critical\")),\n    DSCritical=countif(EventLog==\"Directory Service\" and EventID in (1311, 1388, 1925, 2042, 1866)),\n    LastActivity=max(TimeGenerated),\n    FirstActivity=min(TimeGenerated)\n  by Computer\n| extend DFSRHealth=case(\n    DFSRCritical > 0, \"Critical\",\n    DFSRErrors > 0, \"Degraded\",\n    DFSRTotal > 0, \"Active\",\n    \"No Data\"\n  )\n| extend NTFRSHealth=case(\n    NTFRSCritical > 0, \"Critical\",\n    NTFRSErrors > 0, \"Degraded\",\n    NTFRSTotal > 0, \"Active\",\n    \"No Data\"\n  )\n| extend DSHealth=case(\n    DSCritical > 0, \"Critical\",\n    DSErrors > 0, \"Degraded\",\n    DSTotal > 0, \"Active\",\n    \"No Data\"\n  )\n| extend OverallHealth=case(\n    DFSRCritical > 0 or NTFRSCritical > 0 or DSCritical > 0, \"Critical\",\n    DFSRErrors > 0 or NTFRSErrors > 0 or DSErrors > 0, \"Degraded\",\n    TotalEvents > 0, \"Active\",\n    \"No Data\"\n  )\n| order by DFSRCritical desc, NTFRSCritical desc, DSCritical desc, TotalEvents desc\n| project Computer, OverallHealth, DFSRHealth, NTFRSHealth, DSHealth, DFSRCritical, NTFRSCritical, DSCritical, TotalEvents, FirstActivity, LastActivity",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "DC Health Scorecard - DFSR / NTFRS / Directory Service",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "OverallHealth",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "colors",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "Critical",
                          "representation": "redBright",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "Degraded",
                          "representation": "yellow",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "Active",
                          "representation": "green",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "gray",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "DFSRHealth",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "colors",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "Critical",
                          "representation": "redBright",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "Degraded",
                          "representation": "yellow",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "Active",
                          "representation": "green",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "gray",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "NTFRSHealth",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "colors",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "Critical",
                          "representation": "redBright",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "Degraded",
                          "representation": "yellow",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "Active",
                          "representation": "green",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "gray",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "DSHealth",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "colors",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "Critical",
                          "representation": "redBright",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "Degraded",
                          "representation": "yellow",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "Active",
                          "representation": "green",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "gray",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "DFSRCritical",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "redBright"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "NTFRSCritical",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "orange"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "DSCritical",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "purple"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "TotalEvents",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "blue"
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "sortBy": [
                  {
                    "itemKey": "DFSRCritical",
                    "sortOrder": 2
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "dcmatrix-stacked-errors",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog in (\"DFS Replication\",\"File Replication Service\",\"Directory Service\")\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| where EventLevelName in (\"Error\",\"Critical\")\n| summarize\n    DFSR=countif(EventLog==\"DFS Replication\"),\n    NTFRS=countif(EventLog==\"File Replication Service\"),\n    DS=countif(EventLog==\"Directory Service\")\n  by Computer\n| top 30 by (DFSR + NTFRS + DS) desc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Error Count Comparison - All DCs Stacked by Source",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "barchart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "showLegend": true,
                "seriesLabelSettings": [
                  {
                    "seriesName": "DFSR",
                    "color": "red"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "NTFRS",
                    "color": "orange"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "DS",
                    "color": "purple"
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "dcmatrix-hourly-heatmap",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog in (\"DFS Replication\",\"File Replication Service\",\"Directory Service\")\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| where EventLevelName in (\"Error\",\"Critical\")\n| summarize ErrorCount=count() by Computer, bin(TimeGenerated, 1h)\n| summarize\n    AvgErrorsPerHour=round(avg(ErrorCount), 1),\n    MaxErrorsInHour=max(ErrorCount),\n    TotalErrors=sum(ErrorCount),\n    ActiveHours=dcount(bin(TimeGenerated, 1h))\n  by Computer\n| order by TotalErrors desc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "DC Error Rate Summary - Average / Max / Total per Hour",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "AvgErrorsPerHour",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "yellowRed"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "MaxErrorsInHour",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "redBright"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "TotalErrors",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "red"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "50"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "dcmatrix-first-last",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog in (\"DFS Replication\",\"File Replication Service\",\"Directory Service\")\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| summarize\n    TotalEvents=count(),\n    FirstEvent=min(TimeGenerated),\n    LastEvent=max(TimeGenerated),\n    UniqueDays=dcount(startofday(TimeGenerated)),\n    UniqueEventIDs=dcount(EventID)\n  by Computer\n| extend HoursSinceLastEvent=round(datetime_diff(\"minute\", now(), LastEvent) / 60.0, 1)\n| extend SilentStatus=case(\n    HoursSinceLastEvent > 24, \"Critical - Silent > 24h\",\n    HoursSinceLastEvent > 6, \"Warning - Silent > 6h\",\n    \"Active\"\n  )\n| order by LastEvent asc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "DC Activity - First / Last Event and Silent DCs",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "SilentStatus",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "colors",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "Silent > 24h",
                          "representation": "orange",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "Silent > 6h",
                          "representation": "yellow",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "green",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "TotalEvents",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "blue"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "HoursSinceLastEvent",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "yellowRed"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "50"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "dcmatrix-replication-timeline-per-dc",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog in (\"DFS Replication\",\"File Replication Service\",\"Directory Service\")\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| where EventLevelName in (\"Error\",\"Critical\")\n| summarize ErrorCount=count() by Computer, bin(TimeGenerated, 1h)\n| order by TimeGenerated asc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Per-DC Error Volume Over Time (Top DCs in Legend)",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "linechart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "showLegend": true
              }
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": 12,
      "name": "group-logvolume",
      "conditionalVisibility": {
        "parameterName": "Tab",
        "comparison": "isEqualTo",
        "value": "LogVolume"
      },
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "## Log Volume and Cost Estimation\nIngestion is calculated from billable `Event` records only (`_IsBillable=true`) using `_BilledSize`.\nVolume uses decimal GB: `sum(_BilledSize) / 1,000,000,000`.\nCost = `VolumeGB x PricePerGB` (default $2.76), and 30-day projection = `DailyAvgGB x 30 x PricePerGB`.",
              "style": "info"
            },
            "name": "logvolume-header"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "logvolume-kpis",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "let pricePerGB = 2.76;\nlet bytesPerGB = 1000000000.0;\nlet base = Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog in (\"DFS Replication\",\"File Replication Service\",\"Directory Service\")\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| where tolower(tostring(coalesce(_IsBillable, \"true\"))) == \"true\"\n| extend BilledBytes=todouble(coalesce(_BilledSize, 0.0));\nlet totalBytes = toscalar(base | summarize sum(BilledBytes));\nlet totalEvents = toscalar(base | count);\nlet totalGB = totalBytes / bytesPerGB;\nlet daysObserved = toscalar(base | summarize dcount(startofday(TimeGenerated)));\nlet normalizedDays = iff(daysObserved < 1, 1.0, todouble(daysObserved));\nlet dailyAvgGB = totalGB / normalizedDays;\nlet projected30DayGB = dailyAvgGB * 30.0;\nlet estimatedCostUSD = totalGB * pricePerGB;\nlet projected30DayCostUSD = projected30DayGB * pricePerGB;\nlet avgKBPerEvent = iff(totalEvents == 0, 0.0, (totalBytes / 1000.0) / totalEvents);\nprint Metric=\"Total Billed GB\", Value=round(totalGB, 4)\n| union (print Metric=\"Estimated Cost USD\", Value=round(estimatedCostUSD, 2))\n| union (print Metric=\"Daily Average GB\", Value=round(dailyAvgGB, 4))\n| union (print Metric=\"Projected 30-Day GB\", Value=round(projected30DayGB, 4))\n| union (print Metric=\"Projected 30-Day Cost USD\", Value=round(projected30DayCostUSD, 2))\n| union (print Metric=\"Average KB per Event\", Value=round(avgKBPerEvent, 2))",
              "size": 4,
              "title": "Log Volume and Cost KPIs",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "tiles",
              "tileSettings": {
                "showBorder": true,
                "titleContent": {
                  "columnMatch": "Metric",
                  "formatter": 1
                },
                "leftContent": {
                  "columnMatch": "Value",
                  "formatter": 12,
                  "formatOptions": {
                    "palette": "auto"
                  },
                  "numberFormat": {
                    "unit": 17,
                    "options": {
                      "style": "decimal",
                      "maximumFractionDigits": 4
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "name": "logvolume-daily-trend",
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Event\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventLog in (\"DFS Replication\",\"File Replication Service\",\"Directory Service\")\n| where \"value::all\" in ({Computers}) or Computer in ({Computers})\n| where tolower(tostring(coalesce(_IsBillable, \"true\"))) == \"true\"\n| extend BilledGB=todouble(coalesce(_BilledSize, 0.0)) / 1000000000.0\n| summarize TotalGB=round(sum(BilledGB), 4) by bin(TimeGenerated, 1d), EventLog\n| order by TimeGenerated asc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Daily Billed GB by Log Source",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "areachart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "showLegend": true
              }
            }
          },
